snippet.title: Beast - Exclusive Announcement Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description:
Watch the announcement trailer for Beast, an isometric RPG game developed using Unreal Engine 5. Explore a dark, medieval world, torn by plague and military conflicts. Use the beast inside of you to win in battle, but be careful to not let it consume you. Beast is coming to PC at a later date.

#IGN #Gaming
